{
  "stem": "3022.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When we heard about the advancing-- through the contacts with the underground-- about the advancing Russian army, a group of us young people, we had a tunnel dug from the camp to the outside.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the last minute decision we made was not to use it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because the most that could escape was 20, 25 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we felt that we're going to jeopardize hundreds of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we didn't know whether we're going to survive, but we surely will sign a death edict for many people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we did not use the escape route.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were loaded on trains, and we were taken to Wieliczka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Wieliczka was a salt mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They had a salt mine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The camp was around the salt mine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was one part of the camp was for the women, and one part was for the men.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Several weeks later, all the people from our camp were rounded up and put on the transport.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going, but we assumed that we're either going to one of the extermination camps or another labor camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And under conditions such as we lived, you develop a very keen sense of being able to determine whom you can trust, who are the people that, when push comes to pull, will not betray you.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we tried to surround ourselves with those people, and go into the trains with that group of people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But that was impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So you had maybe 20 or 25 people in the particular car that were friendly with you, and the rest were other people.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
